      "iconName": "Ninjutsu:_Petal_Barrage",
      "tips": "The Scarlet Shadow’s secret technique. When Hanabi has full HP, health that would have been granted from Lifesteal is converted into a shield. When this shield is active, Hanabi is immune to all control effects.",
