    "skill1": {
      "name": "Ninjutsu: Equinox",
      "description": "(Passive): The secret Ninjutsu of the Scarlet Shadow makes Hanabi immune to control effects when she has a shield from any source. (Active): Hanabi gains a 300( +40% Total Physical Attack) shield for 5s. When the shield is active, Hanabi gains 20% Movement Speed and 25% Attack Speed, and 20% of her damage dealt to enemy heroes will be added to this shield (only adds 10% of the damage dealt to non-hero units). This shield cannot exceed 50% of Hanabi's max HP.",
