      "iconName": "Ninjutsu:_Soul_Scroll",
      "tips": "Fires a kunai in the specified direction, attached with a scroll sealed by demonic flower energy. Deals physical damage to enemies it hits along the way and slows them. Hanabi will recover Mana for each enemy hero hit (this Mana regeneration effect will decay when hitting multiple heroes).",
      "iconUrl": "/raw-assets/skill_icons/hanabi/ninjutsu_soul_scroll.png",
      "displayLabel": "Skill 2",
      "skillSlot": "skill2"
    },
    "ultimate": {
      "name": "Forbidden Jutsu: Higanbana",
      "description": "Hanabi throws Higanbana in the targeted direction, dealing 300( +50% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to the first enemy hero hit and immobilizing them for 0.8s. After 1s, Higanbana will bloom at the location of the first hit, dealing 300( +50% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) to nearby enemies. Subsequent hits on the same target decay to 20% damage.",
